  345|       |    // had already parsed items before Debug ran — nested calls always start
  346|       |    // with `parsed == 0` because nested Series are freshly constructed by
  347|       |    // parse_value. Use it to emit a leading `...` marker so the reader can
  348|       |    // see this rendering does not start at item zero.
